high_descs: Turn and go to the table on the side where the trash bag is on the floor.
Pick up the knife that is to the left of the bowl on the table.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the counter that is to the left of the stove.
With the knife slice the potato that is on the counter.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the knife in.  Close the door and start the microwave.
Turn and go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up a middle slice of potato that you just sliced.
With the potato slice in hand turn and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave.  Put the slice of potato behind he knife and shut the door. Start the microwave. When done open it and grab the potato slice.
With the potato slice in hand turn and turn and go to the table on the side where the trash bag is on the floor.
Place the potato slice on the table in front of the white coffee mug and to the right of it.
anns.task_desc: Slice potato to warm up slice and place on table.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the table on the right
Pick up knife from table
Turn right, then left, walk to counter left of the stove
Cut the potato into slices
Turn right, walk to the microwave
Open the microwave door, place knife inside, close door
Walk back to the counter that has the potato
Pick up slice of potato
Walk back to the microwave,
Open the microwave, place potato inside, close door, turn on
Remove cooked potato, turn around, walk to the table behind you
Place potato slice on table
Turn right and walk across the room and turn right to face the end of the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Walk to the right of the table across the room to face the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Step to the right and look up to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave and shut it.
Step to the left to face the potato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Step the right and look up to face the microwave.
Heat the slice of potato in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and cross the room, then turn right and cross the room and face the end of the table on the right.
Place the potato slice on the end of the table.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato slice and place it on the end of the table.

high_descs: Turn around and approach the table by the window
Pick up the knife next the the blue bowl from the table
Turn and walk over to the kitchen counter left of the oven
Cut the potato on the counter using the knife
Turn right and approach the microwave oven above the stove
Put the knife into the microwave
Turn left and return to the counter with the potato on it
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter
Turn and walk back over to the microwave
Put the potato slice into the microwave and cook it
Take the potato out of the microwave and walk over to the table
Put the potato on the table in front of the blue bowl
anns.task_desc: Place the cooked potato on the table

high_descs: Turn to the right and approach the white table across the room.
Pick up the knife next to the blue bowl.
Turn to the right and walk across the room to the brown counter on the left of the stove.
Slice the potato laying on the counter.
Go to the stove.
Put the knife in the microwave above the stove.
Go back to the brown counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Go right to the microwave above the stove.
Put the potato in the microwave, cook it with the knife and take the potato back out.
Turn around and take the cooked potato to the white table across the room on your right.
Put the cooked potato slice on the table to the right of the spatula and in front of the white mug and blue bowl.
anns.task_desc: Cook a piece of sliced potato in the microwave with a knife.

high_descs: Turn right, walk straight towards the trash bag, turn right towards the white table.
Get the knife that is in the middle of the mug and bowl.
Turn right, then turn left and walk to the counter top to the left of the stove.
Cut the potato into slices.
Go to the right in front of the stove
Put the knife in the microwave.
Go to the left to the counter top next to the stove.
Get a slice of potato.
Go to the right in front of the stove.
Put the slice of potato into the microwave. Turn on the microwave, take the slice of potato from the microwave.
Turn around, walk straight. Turn right, walk straight towards the trash bag, turn right towards the white table.
Put the slice of potato on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of potato on the white table.
